Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(626.667,523.333)}宾夕法尼亚州\N阿米什乡村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,574)}北极光营地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.63,0:00:01.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,僵尸国度前景提要\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Previously on Z Nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642.667,464.667)}感染控制应急总部 麦克林 弗吉尼亚\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,都是僵尸咬的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Those are zombie bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:04.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有八个\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Eight of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:07.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们可以把他带到加利福尼亚的实验室\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}If we can get him to the lab in California,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:09.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们就可以研究他的血做更多的疫苗了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}they can use his blood and make more of the vaccine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:11.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-射死他 -\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}- Shoot him! -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:14.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你就是那个救了我小命的神枪手吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You're that sharp shooter that saved my ass, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:16.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你叫什么 小子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}So what's your name, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:18.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一万\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Ten Thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Does it mean anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:21.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要杀死的僵尸数\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}How many zombies I'm going to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:22.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:25.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,1059\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}One thousand fifty-nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:30.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,1060\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}One thousand sixty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:31.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,干得好 小子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Nice shot, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:49.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,阿曼门诺派的僵尸\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Amish zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,搞什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:52.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,逗我吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:53.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们以自我隔离\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}They tried to quarantine themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:54.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,来和其他的团体分开\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}from the rest of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:56.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,防止僵尸病毒的传染\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Keep the Zs from spreading the infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:00:58.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那也是罗梅罗沦陷以前的事儿了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}That was before we knew Romero had it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们都携带着病毒\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We were all carrying the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:02.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是谁 怎么死的都不重要了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Didn't matter who you were or how you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:06.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,活死人之夜 看电影还不错 真变这样也太衰了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Night of the Living Dead. Great movie, sucky reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:10.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我一直没搞懂 如果不是僵尸传播了病毒\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You know what I don't get, If the Zs didn't spread the virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:12.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为什么我们全部感染了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}how did we all get infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:14.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我听过的最靠谱的说是通过鸟来传播\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Best guess I heard, it was spread by birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:17.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,以鸟类病毒的寄生虫为载体\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Some kind of parasite piggybacked on the bird flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只要你活着 就一直潜藏在你体内\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Stays dormant 'till you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:20.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,要我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:22.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这个有亲身体验的人来说的话\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}take it from somebody who knows first hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:24.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,事实是他们变成僵尸以后\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Other than the fact that they find brains delicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就只想着美味的脑花了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}when it comes to zombies nobody knows nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:31.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,轮到我了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:39.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还是不是朋友了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Have we just met?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:42.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:43.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 快点\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Hey, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:44.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想在天黑前通过华盛顿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I want to get past DC before dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:45.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:48.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我说 他们什么都没有\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I'm tellin' ya, there ain't nothin' there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有思维 没有记忆\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}No thoughts, no memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:52.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有灵魂\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}No soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:52.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:54.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们也不算是死了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Well they're not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:55.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们没放弃追求\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}They want something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:57.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 追求脑髓\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Yeah. Brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:00.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果你没有灵魂\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You can't want something if you're not conscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:01.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当你神志不清时 你就不会有追求了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}if you don't have a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我爸爸受伤的时候\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}When my pa was wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他告诉我在他转变前把他捆起来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}he told me to tie him up before he turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:10.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让我发誓在他死后帮他一把\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Made me promise to show him mercy when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:12.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,打他的头部 你知道吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Kill the brain, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:15.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我做不到\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:16.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我下不了手\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I couldn't hurt my pa,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:19.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不管他变成了什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}no matter what he'd become.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:23.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我凝视他的眼睛 我看了那么久\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I stared into his eyes for the longest time, just
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:26.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,希望能从他的眼里看出一丝他自己的样子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}looking for some sign he was still in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:27.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你看到了吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Did you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:31.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你后来怎么办的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:33.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我杀了它\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可恶 小子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Damn, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:36.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你居然放倒了你自己的老爸\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You had to put down your own dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:37.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我没有杀他\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:39.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是它 宝盖头的它\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:41.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但如果没有生命 你要怎么杀死它\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}But if it's not alive, how did you kill it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:42.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一刀刺穿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Piked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:46.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就是这里 那是我杀的第一个僵尸\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Right here. My first kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:49.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我总是祈祷他明白\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I always wish he knew, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:52.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我也算实现了我的承诺\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}somehow knew that I kept my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:12.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有人 六点钟方向\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Humans! Six o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看到了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:25.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,又是你的食人族朋友么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Is that more of your cannibal friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:27.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 是别人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}No. Something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:27.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,前面\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:35.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他去哪\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Where's he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 小子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Hey! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么办\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:40.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,压过去吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Plow right through?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:44.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 我不想再把卡车弄坏了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}No, I don't want to wreck the truck again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:45.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,下去解决掉他们 再赶路\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Let's pike them and be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:48.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么 我们在开慈善晚宴吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Oh what, are we having a little mercy party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 低调一点\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Hey, let's do this quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:52.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,附近可能还会有更多丧尸\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}There might be more of them nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:01.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,等等 等等\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有点不对劲\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,恩 她说的对 看他们的脚\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Yeah, she's right. Look at their feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:13.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,呆在那别动\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:17.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 要么扔掉你的武器\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}All right, now drop your weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,要么死\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}or die
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:21.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一点都不含糊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}right where you stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,放下武器\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Put down the weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:27.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,要么就等着变僵尸吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}or eat brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:37.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,天啊 好小子 我喜欢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}God, I love that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:40.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在 我们只想要那个车\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Now, we just want the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:41.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好不\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把卡车给我们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}So give us the truck
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:46.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就饶你们不死\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}and we'll let you live to die another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:47.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,给他们卡车\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Give them the truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:49.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么也别给他们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Don't give them a goddamn thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,加内特 好好算算\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Do the math Garnett.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:53.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们还有更重要的事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We have other priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:55.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就给他们那个破卡车吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Get them the damn truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:00.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,听你朋友的吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Listen to your friend there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:03.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有人想死\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Nobody wants to die.
