Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:24.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我猜的话\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,九级以上可进入安全机密\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Level nine top secret clearance only.
