Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,单身\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}single.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:04.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,啊不对 状态是未知\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I mean, status unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:09.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}What a tomato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:22.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:25.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,无意冒犯啊宝贝 你真该洗个澡了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}No offense babe, but you need a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:26.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦 好啊 那你上次换内裤\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Oh, okay. Yeah, when was the last time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是什么时候 混小子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}you changed your underwear goat-boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么内裤\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}What underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,真恶心\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Ewww!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:37.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:38.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们看得到了吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Y'all see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就是他们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}That's them, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:41.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:48.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看上去这次他们是想抢劫平民家庭了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Looks like they're trying to rob some poor family this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要是插手的话他们就别想了 来吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Not if I have anything to say about it. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:53.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我能不能说 别这么干\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Would it matter at all if I said don't do this?
