Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:59.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不然我就打爆你的头\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}or the first shot takes your head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:02.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你也听到了 快放下武器\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You heard the man. Drop your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,快\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:21.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是什么情况\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:23.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,抢劫\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}A robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,放下武器\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Drop your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:36.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,赶紧的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,别逼我把你们也杀了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I don't want to have to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:02.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,再也不能冒险了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Never get out of the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 这玩意儿能再慢一点吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Yo, can't this thing go any faster?
