Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:20.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,每次和你说话都让我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Talking to you makes me wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对这次拯救人类之行感到更加迷茫\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}about this whole saving humanity thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:24.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,停车\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是那一家子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Oh, it's the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:44.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们不能再在这条路上走了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We got to get off this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:50.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,完全没有任何新鲜事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Absolutley nothing new is going on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还会发生在这个日趋败落的世界\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}in this decimated world of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看哪儿都是一样的绝望\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}It's the same desperation, the same devastation
