Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:10.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,别叫\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我是查理加内特中士 呼叫北极光营地\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}This is Sergeant Charles Garnett calling Northern Light.
