Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:30.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,能看到我吗 z市民 你在吗 完毕\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Can you read me? Citizen Z, are you there? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在 这里是北极光营地\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Yes, this is Northern Light for Garnett.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:35.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,z市民回复中 加内特请说\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Citizen Z hitting you back. Go for Garnett.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,太好了 我们在这东西上花了几个小时了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Thank God. We've been trying to make this work for hours.
