Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们的队员卡弗 在得来速汽车餐厅找到的摄像头\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}One of our team, Carver jerry-rigged a drive-thru camera
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:46.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,艾迪 卡弗吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Addy Carver?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她在吗 我想打个招呼\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Is she there? I wanna say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦 好啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 安迪\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Hi, Addy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你那边怎么样啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}How's it going down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,额 一团糟\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Ummm, it's pretty eff'd up actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:06.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你那边怎么样啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}How's it going wherever you are?
