Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:17.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,能不能趁僵尸还没找到咱们 麻利点\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Could we please get on with this before the Zs find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:20.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,等等 那是墨菲吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Wait. Is that Murphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Outstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:26.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,很高兴你还活着 先生\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Glad to see you're still alive, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我们要是再不离开这条高速路就活不了了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Yeah but he won't be for long if we don't get off this highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:30.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们急需其他的交通方式\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We're in desperate need of alternate transpo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们要飞机 直升机或者热气球\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We're looking for an airplane or a chopper or a hot air balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:34.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,能飞的就行\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Anything airborne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这倒是有一个\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}There is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我最近都有检测到\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I've been monitoring some random transmissions
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,从感染控制应急总部\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}from what's left of the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,传来的信号\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Emergency Headquarters for Infection Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我能听到 但他们老是不回答我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I can hear them, but they don't respond when I reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:45.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,挺混乱的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}And it's pretty garbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,迈侃多斯上将可能还被困在那儿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}General McCandles might still be holed up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:51.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,算你们走运\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我能看到那里有一辆直升机\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I have a visual confirmation on that chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看起来还在那儿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}It looks like it's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:56.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在哪儿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:13:00.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,弗吉尼亚的麦克林 在华盛顿特区的西边\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}McLean, Virginia. Twenty clicks due west of Washington DC.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:02.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,找找一栋被严重破坏的高楼\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Look for a high-rise with structural damage
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:03.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,楼顶上停着一辆直升机\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}and a chopper on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那得向南走几百里呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Now that's a hundred miles south from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:06.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们要去西边 不是南边\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We're going west, not south.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,西边 你到底还想不想离开这高速路了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}West. Do you want to get off the road or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:10.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}- Puppies and kittens! -
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们得撤了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:12.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,再见 艾迪森\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Bye, Addison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:15.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,到了记得联系我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Call me when you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:19.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,比我想象中差一点\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Not exactly what I was hoping for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这年头你要学会万事不要抱太大希望\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}One of these days you're gonna learn to quit hoping for things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当我们把你丢在马路边的时候\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You better hope not
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:57.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你才最好不要抱什么希望\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}cuz that's when we leave your ass at the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:02.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,停 报上名来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Halt! Who goes there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:04.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我是查理 加内特中士 国民警卫队的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Sergeant Charles Garnett, National Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是罗伯塔沃伦中尉\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}This is Lieutenant Roberta Warren,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,- 来干什么的 - 他也是国民警卫队的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}- State your business. - also National Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们正在执行一个高级任务\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We're on a high priority mission
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:13.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,要将这个人带到加利福尼亚的疾病控制中心实验室\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}to get this man to a CDC lab in California.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们是国家安全局的人派来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We were sent here by an Intell Officer from the NSA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,找麦坎多斯上校的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}to see General McCandles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:19.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要他帮我们找交通工具\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We need his help finding transpo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:20.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们听说他有一辆直升机\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We were told he has a helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是 他是有\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Yeah, he's got a chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但麦坎多斯上校是个大忙人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}But General McCandles is a very busy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他还有一整个东海岸要管\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}He's got the entire east coast under his command.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没空搭理一堆要去送死的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}He can't worry about some raggedy ass group of civilians
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:30.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,衣衫褴褛的平民组织\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}on a suicide mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我建议你们最好趁僵尸还没发现你们之前逃命吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I suggest you move on before the infected find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:37.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,长官 我们可不是什么衣衫褴褛的平民组织\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Nothing raggedy ass about this group of civilians, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这个男人身上带着\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}And this man has important information
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:42.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,抵抗僵尸病毒的重要信息\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}about a vaccine for the zombie virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他闻着一股僵尸味儿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}He smells like a damn Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:02.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,说得跟你很好闻一样\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You don't smell so good yourself, septic tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:05.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你到底帮不帮我们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You gonna help us or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们想见上校\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You want to see the General?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你们得贡献点什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You're going to have to pay a tribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,以表诚意\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Gesture of goodwill to show him you're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你想要什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}What kind of tribute you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们的药品已经断了一年了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Our medic has been MIA over a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:19.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要止痛药 抗生素\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We need painkillers. Antibiotics.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么都行\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Anything you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:25.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我去拿包\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I'll get my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:30.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我有阿司匹林 四环素 环丙沙星\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I got aspirin, tetracycline, cipro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:33.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,足够抵挡多重感染了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}That should knock out most any infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:36.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有奥斯康定\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}And oxycontin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:39.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,奥斯康定 我们需要止痛药\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}The oxy. We need painkillers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还要不要见上校了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You want to see the General or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:54.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们就这么点儿了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}This is the last of our supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}That'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:19.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我这就带你们去见上校\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}The General will see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:21.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么要浪费我的时间\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Why are you wasting my time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,麦坎多斯上校\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}General McCandles, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这里有个国民警卫小队和几个平民\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We have a National Guard unit and several civilians
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:27.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,想和你谈一谈\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}requesting permission to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们带来上帝了吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Is sweet Jesus with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:30.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,- 那叫他们去死-  - 不太可能\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}- Then tell them to go to hell! - I don't believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我还要打仗呢 我呼叫的空援呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I've got a war to fight! Where's that close air support I ordered
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:36.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,告诉海军上将我要那些潜艇全部就位\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Tell the Admiral I need those subs in position by 0800.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,兄弟们 不惜一切守住阵地\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Bravo Company, hold your position at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不惜一切\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Repeat, all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们也听到了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You heard the General.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:44.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,麦坎多斯上校\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}General McCandles, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们直接受命于总统\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We're on a mission of extreme importance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:50.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,执行这项高级任务\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}by direct order from the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:53.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这事儿十万火急 我们必须飞去威尔逊山的疾病控制中心实验室\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}It's imperative that we find air transport to Mt. Wilson CDC lab
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,- 不好意思我很忙- 那可是在加州\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}- Sorry, I'm busy. - in California.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的援军呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Where are my reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:57.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你也听到了 快走吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You heard the man. Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你把我的奥斯康定都吐出来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I've a good mind to make you barf up my oxycontin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:03.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,医师 别冲动\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Doc! Doc! Stand down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你刚才是说 医师吗 就是医生那个医师吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Did you say Doc? As in doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我们小队里有个医生\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Yeah, our team includes a medical doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为什么不早说 把他叫上来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Why didn't you say so? Send him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我这儿有个病员需要治疗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I have a wounded man in need of medical attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:20.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只能医生上去 你们在下面等着\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Just the doctor. The rest of you wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我行的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:23.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:27.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 嘿 跟他说直升飞机的事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Hey, hey, hey. Talk to him about the chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:43.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,狗娘养的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:46.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我可是打算把那些奥克康定留着以后到加州聚会时嗨的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I was saving that oxy for a party when we got to Cali.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你就是那个医生吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You the medic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,正是在下\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I am indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:56.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是上校吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You the General?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,亚瑟 C 麦坎多斯 指挥中心的指挥官\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}General Arthur C. McCandles. Commander, Central Command,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,感染反应部队\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Infection Response Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,受伤的人呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Where's your wounded man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这儿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是被咬了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}It's not a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看起来很糟糕\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}This looks bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,真的很糟糕\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Real bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只是小抓伤\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:35.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 这 这更像是坏死了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}No, that's... that's more like gangrene.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:38.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,能保住这条腿吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Can you save the leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,恐怕不行了 上校\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I'm afraid not, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:41.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,已经开始蔓延了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}It's already starting to spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:44.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,很快僵尸病毒就会袭遍全身\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Soon the Z virus will take over.
