Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.94,0:36:24.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们正在执行一个事关人类生死任务\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We're on a mission that just might save the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.28,0:36:26.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这个人血液里有种抗体\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}This man has antibodies in his blood
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.74,0:36:28.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可以做成僵尸疫苗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}needed to make a zombie vaccine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.66,0:36:32.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们被要求把他送到加州疾病防治中心的实验室\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We've been tasked with getting him to a CDC lab in California.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.33,0:36:33.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,必须要活的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.41,0:36:35.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要你的直升机\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We need your helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.71,0:36:41.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们干嘛不早说\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Well hell, why didn't you say so sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.80,0:36:44.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我会亲自把你们送去\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I'll fly you there myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.84,0:36:48.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她很漂亮 不是吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}She's beautiful, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.26,0:36:50.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是个啥 逗我们吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}What is this, some kind of joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.72,0:36:53.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她的确需要点保养 不过\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Sure, she needs a little maintenance. But,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.39,0:36:55.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,细心看护\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}with some TLC,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.35,0:36:57.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,再找一些备用的零件\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}a little help scrounging a few spare parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.35,0:36:59.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,马上就可以让你们到加州了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I'll have you to California in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.23,0:36:59.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.82,0:37:00.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.98,0:37:02.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我一个朋友为了这堆破铜烂铁送命了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}A friend of mine died trying to get to that pile of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.86,0:37:04.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你和多克是朋友吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You and Doc were friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.20,0:37:06.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一起打过牌 虽然只有一次\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We played cards... once.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.53,0:37:08.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就是战争 孩子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}This is war, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.37,0:37:10.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们失去了很多朋友\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We've all lost friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.03,0:37:11.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所有我认识的人都死了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Hell, everybody I ever knew is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.62,0:37:13.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一点也不稀奇\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Why am I not surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.33,0:37:14.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不怎么喜欢你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You know I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.50,0:37:15.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不喜欢我的人多了去了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Well get in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.50,0:37:16.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,麦坎多斯上将\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}General McCandles.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.37,0:37:18.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,长官\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.63,0:37:21.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,感谢你的好意 不过我们得找别的交通工具了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Thank you, but I think we'll find alternate transportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.21,0:37:23.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得我疯了 是吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You think I'm insane, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.05,0:37:31.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许我真疯了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Well maybe I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.06,0:37:34.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,太多人死去\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Too much death.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.77,0:37:37.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,太多好人英年早逝\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Too many good men sent to an early grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.94,0:37:43.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,太多僵尸\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Too many zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.20,0:37:48.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,退下 让我来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Stand down! I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.41,0:37:52.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,来吧 你们这群吃人的败类\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Come here you Godless brain eating scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.24,0:37:54.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.20,0:37:56.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我要把你们拉入地狱\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I'll see you in Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.51,0:38:12.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,多克呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}What happened to Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.60,0:38:17.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他没能逃过这一劫\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}He didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.27,0:38:26.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,僵尸来了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.61,0:38:28.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Oh, whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.53,0:38:31.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,天呐 那不是\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Oh God, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.20,0:38:33.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是多克\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}It's Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.54,0:38:41.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们必须\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Someone's gotta...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.92,0:38:42.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我来吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.63,0:38:49.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,史蒂芬 多克 贝克\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Steven "Doc" Beck.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.38,0:38:54.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,愿你安息\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I give you mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.23,0:39:01.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你他妈干嘛 沃伦\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}What the hell, Warren?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.73,0:39:03.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你想杀死我吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You trying to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.86,0:39:05.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还活着\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.98,0:39:07.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我当然还活着\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Damn straight I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.74,0:39:12.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们都以为你死了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}We thought you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.99,0:39:14.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我也以为我死了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Well so did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.74,0:39:19.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有个傻子朝我被卡住的通风井扔了个手榴弹\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Some numbskull threw a grenade in the air shaft I was stuck in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.21,0:39:23.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,快过来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Well hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.17,0:39:23.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.83,0:39:25.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.00,0:39:26.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,啵一个吧 宝贝\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Give me a kiss, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.22,0:39:38.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我得走了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Well I should let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.27,0:39:39.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你一直忙着注意\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I'm sure you're busy with
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.60,0:39:43.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,世界各地的情况\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}keeping an eye on the world and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.85,0:39:45.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.27,0:39:48.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的狗狗饿了 我必须给它喂食\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I got a hungry dog here I better go feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.28,0:39:50.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,和你聊天很高兴\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Nice talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.19,0:39:52.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,希望我们以后能见面\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I hope we get to meet someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.70,0:39:56.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I'd really like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.62,0:39:57.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.33,0:40:02.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,甜心王子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Sweet prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.29,0:40:06.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,晚安 窈窕淑女\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Good night, fair lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.39,0:40:21.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,接下来给所有寂寞的人送上一首歌\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Here's a song for all the lonely people out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.23,0:40:24.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,送给还存活着的任何人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}which is just about everybody that's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.14,0:40:26.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果有人和你一起度过了世界末日\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}So if you've got somebody to go through the Apocalypse with,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.65,0:40:29.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你一定要好好珍惜\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}you better watch their backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.48,0:40:31.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为没有多人存活了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Cuz there ain't many of us left.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.65,0:40:34.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦 对了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}And oh yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.49,0:40:38.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想把这首歌送给艾迪生 卡弗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I'd like to dedicate this song to Addison Carver,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.78,0:40:41.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不论你在哪\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}wherever you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.58,0:40:45.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想把这首歌送给艾迪生 卡弗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I'd like to dedicate this song to Addison Carver,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.25,0:40:48.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不论你在哪\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}wherever you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.00,0:40:52.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我只跟他说过两次话 拜托\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I talked to the guy twice. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.18,0:40:58.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 孩子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}You know kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.72,0:41:01.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我一直在想你跟我说的关于你爸的事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I've been thinking about what you told me about your dad
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.02,0:41:05.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你多么希望他知道你做了对的事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}and how you wished he knew you did the right thing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.35,0:41:07.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,帮他个忙 就像你答应的那样\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}giving him mercy like you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.06,0:41:07.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.82,0:41:12.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我只是想让你知道\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Well I just want you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.90,0:41:15.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你爸知道你所做的一切\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}your dad knows what you did for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.15,0:41:19.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他知道你做了正确的事 知道你遵守了诺言\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}And he knows you did the right thing. You kept your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.95,0:41:23.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.56,0:41:48.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 爸爸\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I'm sorry, papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.73,0:41:56.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs25}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.94,0:42:39.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
